metadata.name: Ape Fest 2022 Tickets
metadata.description:
Ape Drops is auctioning off a pair of tickets to Ape Fest 2022! Proceeds from the auction will go to Orangutan Outreach (https://redapes.org/cryptorangutan/). The holder of this NFT can redeem 2 tickets. 

Redeem Instructions: To be announced.

Event Date: June 20 - 23, 2022.

Location: New York City. Exact venue location to be announced. 

Lineup: To be announced.
